    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Sancte Trinitatis Domini. Que aput presides ceterosque magistratus
                        geruntur describere pulblice utilitatis est. Advenit igitur <persName><name
                                ref="Heinricus">Henricus</name></persName> adultus filius quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Morus">Moroni</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Palatine_count #Missus_regis" ref="#people/3242"
                            >Tancredo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Palatine_count">sacri palatii comite</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Missus_regis">missus donni imper(…)</rs> (…) in civitate
                            <placeName ref="#places/4" key="#Churches">Luca</placeName> ante
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3221" key="#Churches"><rs
                                key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs> Sancti Donnini</orgName> residente,
                        cum eo <persName key="#Judge"><name ref="Maginfredus"
                            >Manfredus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> et <persName key="#Causidicus"><name
                                ref="Nicolaus">Nicolaus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Causidicus">caus(…)</rs>, a suprascripto comite ut auctoritatem
                        sibi daret vendendi suam portione de duabus petiis de terris que sunt in
                        loco <placeName ref="#places/3107">(…)co ubi dicitur a le Lame</placeName>,
                        pro solvendo debito dotis et antifati cognate sue <persName><name
                                ref="Adalecta">Adaleite</name></persName> que fuit mulier (…)
                        habebat mobilia unde ipsum debitum solvere posset. Quo audito, cum
                        suprascriptus comes diligenter iuspiceret soluti (…) non posset, causa
                        cognita consilio suprascripti Manfredi iudicis et Nicholai causid(…) suo
                        decreto cum auctoritate Uberti filio Gerardi et item (G)ofredi mona(…)
                        (s)icut inferius continetur.</ab>
                    <ab>(…) Iehsu Christi Dei eterni, anno ab incarnatione eius millesimo centesimo
                        quinqua(…), (…)to kal. augusti, indictione quinta. Manifestus sum ego
                        Henricus adultus, filius quondam Moroni, quia per hanc cartulam cum
                        auctoritate <persName><name ref="Hubertus">Uberti</name></persName> filio
                                <persName><name ref="Gherardus">Gerardi</name></persName> et item
                                <persName><name ref="Hubertus">Uberti</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Soffredus">Sofredi</name></persName> tutoribus
                        meis, et ex decreto (T)ancredi sacri palatii comitis et missis donni
                        imperatoris, consilio Manfredi iudicis et Nicholai causidicis, vendo et
                        trado <persName><name ref="Wido">(G)uido</name></persName> rectori <orgName
                            key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs key="#Hospitals"
                                >ospitalis</rs> Sancti Iacobi et Sancti Gilii</orgName> de
                            <placeName key="#Hospitals" ref="#places/3207">Altopascio</placeName>,
                        afficto omni anno decem et octo staria de grano que mihi (…) de triginta
                        staria et medio de riccoltu de duo petis de terris que sunt in loco et
                        finibus <placeName ref="#places/3107">Spinatico ubi dicitur a le
                            Lame</placeName>. Prima (…) unum caput in terra filiorum quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Tabulinus">Thabulini</name></persName> et aliut
                        in terra filiorum quondam <persName><name ref="Strego"
                            >Stregonis</name></persName>, latus unum in terra mea quam tenet
                                <persName><name ref="Brunectus">Bru(…)tus</name></persName> (…) sic
                        termina posita sunt. Et aliut latus tenet in terra <persName><name
                                ref="Widuccius de Trepiatha">Guiducci di
                        Trepiatha</name></persName>. Secunda tenet unum caput in terra <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/272" key="#Churches">Sancte Marie
                            Forisporta</orgName> et aliut in terra meam quam tenet suprascriptus
                                <persName><name ref="Brunectus Tassignanus">Brunectus
                                Tassignanus</name></persName>. Latus unum te(net) in terra
                                <persName><name ref="Gherardinus Piliciani">Gerardini
                                Piliciani</name></persName>, et aliut in terra <persName><name
                                ref="Heinricus">Henrici</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Pallia">Pallie</name></persName>. (…)
                        <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: tredecim lucensis monete, quos dedi pro solvendo
                        suprascripto debito cognate mee Adalette. Et <persName><name ref="Iolicta"
                                >Iulicta</name></persName> relic(…) dedit suprascriptas tredecim
                        libras suprascripto ospitali pro remedio ani(…) sue et remedio ani(…).
                            <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum. (…) Actum Luca. (…) (E)go Tancredus
                        sacri palatii comes et misus donni imperatoris hec apud me acta confirmo.
                        Has scripsit prudens Nicholaus iuris amator. SM (…)chi quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Teudericus">Tederighi</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Baverus">Baveri</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Lambertus">Lanberti</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Vivianus">Viviani</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Hubertus">Uberti</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Galganus">Galgani</name></persName> quondam
                        *** rogati <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>. (S) <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Heinricus">Henricus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Writer #Notary">not.</rs> domni imperatoris, ex decreto
                        suprascripti Tancredi sacri palatii comitis, post traditam complevi et dedi.
                        Et insuper obligo me meosque heredes ad penam librarum viginti optimi
                        argenti et ad penam consulum et treguanorum lucensium qui nunc sunt vel in
                        antea erunt. (…)</ab>
                </div>
